# Privacy Policy

Morning Brief is a personal, single-user application. It reads the
authenticated user's own WHOOP recovery, sleep, and cycle data solely to
generate that user's private daily briefing.

- Data is used only to write the user's own briefing.
- No WHOOP data is sold, shared, or disclosed to any third party.
- No WHOOP data is stored beyond the generated briefing itself.
- Access can be revoked at any time from the user's WHOOP account settings.

